DUV 光刻机的突破，具有怎样的历史意义？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/667459974","type":"question","created":1726618338,"answer_count":308,"follower_count":1112,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[90716,598202,3544139,3713138],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近日，工业和信息化部印发《首台（套）重大技术装备推广应用指导目录（2024 年版）》通知。据“工信微报”介绍，重大技术装备是国之重器，事关综合国力和国家安全。 值得注意的是，在重大技术装备文件列表中包含了国产氟化氪光刻机（110nm），和氟化氩(ArF)光刻机（65nm）的内容。 氟化氪（KrF）和氟化氩（ArF）两种气体均服务于深紫外（DUV）光刻机，产生深紫外光的准分子激光器。并且氟化氩光刻机和氟化氪光刻机两者均属于DUV光刻机。 目前来说，光刻机共经历了五代的发展，从最早的436nm波长，再到第二代光刻机开始使用波长365nm i-line，第三代则是 248nm 的 KrF 激光，第四代就是193nm 波长的ArF光刻机，属于干式DUV光刻机。重大“芯”突破！国产DUV光刻机问世，相关概念股集体大涨-手机金融界工业和信息化部关于印发《首台（套）重大技术装备推广应用指导目录（2024年版）》的通知"},"attached_info":"CkAIhpf8lvenvIJSEAMaCTExMDYwMjE3NyDitai3BjAAONgIQA5yCTY2NzQ1OTk3NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-7f5296bbd39a3e1736622a662c068078_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1727075969.133066","card_id":"Q_664314645","target":{"id":664314645,"title":"孩子抑郁厌学，为什么看了心理医生还是收效甚微？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/664314645","type":"question","created":1723671076,"answer_count":481,"follower_count":508,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[404,3877,8913,12046,15318],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIhpf8lvenvIJSEAMaCTEwOTkwMzA1NSCkxPS1BjAAOPwDQA9yCTY2NDMxNDY0NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f63e76fbd377f670a6b5657b81f2ae87_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1727075969.133326","card_id":"Q